title: Over/Under Rookie Class 2021
itunes:title: Over/Under Rookie Class 2021
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Gregg Rosenthal and Matt Money Smith bring you all of the latest news in the NFL including Eric Fisher joining the Colts (8:06), a potential looming QB controversy with the Vikings (13:30) and the Broncos placing Ja'wuan James on the non-football injury list (17:05). Tim Tebow is back in the league (28:06) and the NFL schedule will be released Wednesday (32:22). The heroes throw out some over/unders for the new rookie class to close the show (43:30).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
